Info:

First install citrus-maven-plugin
 'mvn install'

An example of pom.xml:

<properties>
    <citrus.maven.plugin.version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</citrus.maven.plugin.version>
</properties>
<build>
  <plugins>
    <plugin>
      <groupId>no.citrus.plugin</groupId>
      <artifactId>citrus-maven-plugin</artifactId>
      <version>${citrus.maven.plugin.version}</version>
    </plugin>
  </plugins>
</build>

Run plugin:
 'mvn no.citrus.plugin:citrus-maven-plugin:1.0-SNAPSHOT:test' 
